{"tid":776389,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"689連續第8日狙擊FCC　與納粹猶太人大屠殺相提並論","createTime":"2018-08-12T04:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T06:06:24.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e35d4d3ccea45dcf233585ba2a1d3ac375722d40","tid":776389,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:50:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180812/large/1534043292_cb12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180812%2Flarge%2F1534043292_cb12.jpg&h=826e09d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前特首、全國政協副主席梁振英昨晚連續第8日，在Facebook撰文狙擊外國記者協會（FCC）邀請民族黨召集人陳浩天演講一事，再次提及未在本港立法的基本法23條，又將港獨議題與納粹主義、猶太人大屠殺等相提並論。<br />\n<br />\n帖文以英文撰寫，稱FCC前執委Francis Moriarty曾建議FCC邀請他演講，說明為何任何有關港獨的聲音也要被壓制（any discussion of nationalist sentiment in Hong Kong should be suppressed）。梁振英就指，陳浩天（Andy Chan）及其政黨不只是發聲，而在某些議題上，有平等辯論機會並非辯護理由。<br />\n文中其後舉例指，協會會否邀請宣揚「種族歧視、反猶太主義或納粹主義（racism, anti-semitism or Nazism）人士，又或者聲稱猶太人大屠殺及南京大屠殺（the Holocaust and Nanjing massacre）是虛構的人士？梁稱相信協會不會，並指Francis Moriarty亦不能以會上有持相反人意見講者為由辯護。"},{"pid":"db3d6b3e95fb658f4237ccb1b26c38559e8cf1e3","tid":776389,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:50:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180812/58553368\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180812%2F58553368&d=wJZSepfUpgmTDB9HfkVJR%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=1bde0a98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180812%2F58553368&h=1e036c96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180812/58553368</a>"},{"pid":"8359d95dd0b5559a1345b45e908b974733ef23cc","tid":776389,"uid":51271,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T04:51:26.0